# state/ — two-tier split:
#
#   IGNORED (ephemeral — regenerated every poll, never commit):
state/last-poll.json
#
#   TRACKED (persistent — these ARE committed, do not add them below):
#     state/draft-seen-counts.json   — draft staleness counters (idle-loop accumulates)
#     state/persistent-blockers.json — deadline/blocker registry
#     state/steam-news-baseline.json — Steam AppNews last-seen version
#     state/steam-last-count.txt     — Steam news item count baseline
#     state/deadline-status.json     — computed deadline severity cache
#     state/history/                 — dated state.json snapshots (forensics)
